data.text:
Features newly remastered analog and digital tracks, as well as a booklet containing archival artwork and liner notes by former development team members, including level designer Toyohisa Tanabe. For KOF95, M.Hataya reprised his role while being joined by composers Akihiro Uchida and Pearl Sibakiti.

More music for The King of Fighters...
